<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from the bottom left side of the base of a  <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front, with a relief of a reclining figure, possibly <rs type="decoration" cert="low">sleeping child</rs> or <rs type="decoration" cert="low">eros</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.16</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.23</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.16</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02-0.025</measure>; lunate <term lang="grc-Latn">sigma</term>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date></p>
</div>
